---
title: Cuban Confetti Salad with Kidney Beans and Feta
description: This warm salad infused with the vibrancy of Cuba is sure to have tummies rumbling. We’ve taken all that is edible about Cuba and presented it to you on a platter, in an explosion of confetti-like colour and flavour sure to thrill. Buen provecho!
